Mount the unit on your wall or set it on top of your entertainment center. Works with the Google Assistant.

column8: ['Your TV craves an audio upgrade. - Treat yourself  and your TV  to better audio with 2 full-range speakers built into a low-profile sound bar that delivers 93dB of high-quality, room-filling sound.
